title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 12 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 12 2022
description:
Pfizer exec admits covid shot never tested for stopping transmission. Montage of liberals saying the shot would stop transmission. C&B on the Dahmer show on Netflix. Senator Ron Johnson joins Clay and Buck to tell us what he'll do with the power he'll have if he's reelected and Republicans win control of the Senate. DeSantis reopens Sanibel Causeway in record time. Speech pathologist calls in on Fetterman. Fetterman contradicts himself in interview.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
